      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777469414,
      "updated": 1777469418
    },
    {
      "id": "69f207e900000000002105d6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777469418,
      "updated": 1777469418
    },
    {
      "id": "69f207f200000000002105f7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777469426,
      "updated": 1777469535
    },
    {
      "id": "69f207ed00000000002105d8",
      "text": " OPの最初のカットが素敵だ",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777469421,
      "updated": 1777469421
    },
    {
      "id": "69f207ed00000000002105d9",
      "text": "  漫画内ではたしか上伊那ぼたんさんを見て愛らしいところを愛でるんだが",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777469421,
      "updated": 1777469421
    },
    {
      "id": "69f207ed00000000002105da",
      "text": "  ぼたんさんをよう見る視線って感じ",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777469421,
      "updated": 1777469421
    },
    {
      "id": "69f207ed00000000002105db",
      "text": " うおなんだこのOPおお……",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777469421,
      "updated": 1777469421
    },
    {
      "id": "69f207ed00000000002105dc",
      "text": " 5:05からの音楽が理知的だ",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777469421,
      "updated": 1777469421
    },
    {
      "id": "69f207ed00000000002105dd",
      "text": "  絵と説明と音楽で急に雰囲気が変わった",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777469421,
      "updated": 1777469421
    },
    {
      "id": "69f207ed00000000002105de",
      "text": " ポン! (ガチャガチャのおもちゃを開いたような音)",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777469421,
      "updated": 1777469437
    },
    {
      "id": "69f207ed00000000002105df",
      "text": "  [https://gyazo.com/7457c05646fafd1a726a5364d48aab35]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777469421,
      "updated": 1777469421
    },
    {
      "id": "69f207ed00000000002105e2",
      "text": "  おしゃれだ！",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777469421,
      "updated": 1777469449
    },
    {
      "id": "69f207ed00000000002105e3",
      "text": " 現在感ある",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777469421,
      "updated": 1777469421
    },
    {
      "id": "69f207ed00000000002105e4",
      "text": "  [https://gyazo.com/8c260e5807cb53ae472c363505378935]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777469421,
      "updated": 1777469421
    },
    {
      "id": "69f2080c00000000002105f9",
      "text": "  いまここにいる人間がやり取りしてる感じ",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777469452,
      "updated": 1777469474
    },
    {
      "id": "69f207ed00000000002105e5",
      "text": " 顔がへこたれる方向に向かって、アルミケースが画面左の床に落下する",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777469421,
      "updated": 1777469421
    },
    {
      "id": "69f207ed00000000002105e6",
      "text": "  [https://gyazo.com/979aaa145e5a0041ebdd323377b638e9]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777469421,
      "updated": 1777469421
    },
    {
      "id": "69f207ed00000000002105e7",
      "text": "  下じゃなくても良いものだ",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777469421,
      "updated": 1777469421
    },
    {
      "id": "69f207ed00000000002105e8",
      "text": " 友だちにもらったエフェク……楽器です",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777469421,
      "updated": 1777469421
    },
    {
      "id": "69f207ed00000000002105e9",
      "text": "  共通の知識がない相手に言ってもわからないだろうと途中で言い換えるやつだ",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777469421,
      "updated": 1777469421
    },
    {
      "id": "69f207ed00000000002105ea",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/1b1449ed8b156064dacee4235034b0b3]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777469421,
      "updated": 1777469421
    },
    {
      "id": "69f207ed00000000002105eb",
      "text": "  さっきのはradio head",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777469421,
      "updated": 1777469421
    },
    {
      "id": "69f207ed00000000002105ec",
      "text": "  これはaphex twinだ",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777469421,
      "updated": 1777469421
    },
    {
      "id": "69f207ed00000000002105ed",
      "text": "  [vlzs.icon]には不明な他のレコードどもそういう実際に存在する聞かれているものなんだろう",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777469421,
      "updated": 1777469421
    },
    {
      "id": "69f207ed00000000002105ee",
      "text": "  現実感ある",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777469421,
      "updated": 1777469421
    },
    {
      "id": "69f207ed00000000002105ef",
      "text": " ほんとに眩しい",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777469421,
      "updated": 1777469421
    },
    {
      "id": "69f208730000000000210601",
      "text": "  それとわかる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777469555,
      "updated": 1777469558
    },
    {
      "id": "69f207ed00000000002105f0",
      "text": " 上長?の視界っぽい",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777469421,
      "updated": 1777469575
    },
    {
      "id": "69f207ed00000000002105f1",
      "text": "  [https://gyazo.com/f5899f55c256800e06e234a11c1fecd5]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777469421,
      "updated": 1777469421
    },
    {
      "id": "69f207ed00000000002105f2",
      "text": " 関係ないけど額縁の絵が窓からの外光を反射してる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777469421,
      "updated": 1777469421
    },
    {
      "id": "69f207ed00000000002105f3",
      "text": "  [https://gyazo.com/2b1dce034274253c5f7c4563d6a959fa]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777469421,
      "updated": 1777469421
    },
    {
      "id": "69f20de300000000004cdd06",
      "text": " 大事なところで映像が書き込まれる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
